print('51515.21')
dog
cat
giraffe
cow
255145151515415152
5154151
66565
54154154
51515.21
Printing the ' in the string
In [15]:
print("Dany's dog")
print('''Peter's watch''')
print("""Sucy's cat""")
Dany's dog
Peter's watch
Sucy's cat
Printing the " in the string
In [16]:
print('Dany"s dog')
print('''Peter"s watch''')
print("""Sucy"s cat""")
Dany"s dog
Peter"s watch
Sucy"s cat
Printing the ' and " in string
In [17]:
print('''Peter's dog and Sucy"s cat''')
print("""Peter's dog and Sucy"s cat""")
Peter's dog and Sucy"s cat
Peter's dog and Sucy"s cat
Doing two commands at a time in python shell.
In [18]:
print("Hello");print("Goodbye!")
Hello
Goodbye!
ARGUMENTS
The value we passed into a function.

Adding multiple arguments in print function.
The default separation is space.

In [19]:
print(1,2,3,4)
print("dog","cat","vehicle",123,34354,4324234.34)
1 2 3 4
dog cat vehicle 123 34354 4324234.34
Adding a separation
In [20]:
print(23,224,35646,sep="*")
print("spam","eggs","cat",sep="-")
23*224*35646
spam-eggs-cat
