max() function
In [26]:
print(max(232423,434335,345435,64556465645654,56))
print(max("spam","eggs","dog"))
print(max('a',"A",'B',"b"))
64556465645654
spam
b
min() function
In [27]:
print(min(232423,434335,345435,64556465645654,56))
print(min("spam","eggs","dog"))
print(min('a',"A",'B',"b"))
56
dog
A
In case of string max() and min() work based on the ASCII value of each character in the string. ASCII of A->65 ASCII of a->97

abs() function
Find absolute value of a number
